headline: Strengthening Fundamentals in Mechanical and Electrical Contracting Industry Drive Analyst Sentiment on EMCOR Group (EME)
summary: EMCOR Group, Inc. (NYSE:EME) is one of the best performing S&P 500 stocks in the last five years.
